BT /F1 12 Tf 72 720 Td
(Chapter 3: Safety
Gas odor detected: evacuate the area, shut off the gas supply valve,
and ventilate. Do not operate electrical switches.
Leak at furnace connection: inspect gas valve GV-220-NG fittings
and re-test with soap solution.) Tj 0 -20 Td
ET
